{"tid":870351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畀返啲飲管我啊","createTime":"2018-10-21T05:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T05:44:32.000Z","uid":948,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"330de5a8ccddaa706328e259dac354bff009a342","tid":870351,"uid":948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"走塑還走塑<br />\n洗唔洗行到邊都無飲管啊<br />\n直接用個杯飲真係好核突<br />\n上一手飲完係咁以洗下就畀下個飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住一隻有漬嘅杯真係好唔開胃<br />\n同埋無咗支飲管無得攪杯嘢 <br />\n會變到好難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔想人用膠飲管轉用紙飲管唔得㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係咁環保不如叫所有鋪頭都學下便利店<br />\n唔好主動印單仲好啦"},{"pid":"8e8831b2ce5c807b25c7eadfa54125e1be49bffe","tid":870351,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"外赤唔好整外賣膠盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要外賣加十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}